  "title": "Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Solution Selling for Mobile &amp; Web Application.</li>\n  <li>Identify and develop sales opportunities in Singapore market.</li>\n  <li>Develop plans and sales strategies to increase branding and market share.</li>\n  <li>Prepare sales presentations and solution demonstration.</li>\n  <li>Prepare Sales proposal.</li>\n  <li>Work with Marketing team to develop sales campaigns to target vertical industry.</li>\n  <li>Forecast monthly, quarterly and annual sales revenue and generate timely sales report.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience in Software Solution Selling</li>\n  <li>Good working attitude and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 4 years Software Sales experience</li>\n  <li>IT background preferred.</li>\n</ul>",
