    "description": "<p><strong>OrangeKloud </strong>serves as a leading No-Code Rapid Mobile Application Development Platform (RMAD) catering to both small-to-medium enterprises (SMEs) and large corporations. We disrupt traditional Enterprise Application development with integrated Agile and DevOps practises, enabling faster, smarter and secure application development.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With Orangekloud, you can transform your apps ideas into reality effortlessly, without the barriers of traditional coding practices.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We believe in making technology accessible to all, and our no-code platform allows businesses to unleash their creativity and drive digital transformation.</p>",
